title: War of the Roses: The Cancelled Road Trip
description: Kelly met Michael in the Twin Cities when he was visiting from Idaho for a bachelor party.  He came to visit once since then but has cancelled the two other trips he had planned and has fallen off from texting and calling so she wants to know what's going on.
